dct_title_s: MCTS Bus Stops Milwaukee County, Wisconsin 2018
dct_description_sm: This point data layer represents the MCTS bus stops for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2018. The dataset was originally published by the Milwaukee County Transit System (MCTS) in 2018.
